    "16451151390f67c7d6": {
      "type": "bi-column-text-blocks",
      "blocks": {
        "6f8ee666-7630-4fca-ad06-fb233c61bb05": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Custom Processing",
            "content": "<p>Conditions and resources at origin are not ideal to meet the United States food safety regulations.  We are fully equipped to import from origin and get product ready to eat (RTE) in our SQF certified facility. We have a fully validated micro reduction system and metal check all goods upon arrival. We provide an array of milling, blending, roasting, cleaning and metal check <\/p>",
            "button_label": "Read more",
            "button_link": "shopify:\/\/pages\/services",
            "button_color": "default"
          }
        },
        "dd5f1e38-6d6d-4dd1-ba06-bb0d29acdfeb": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Quality Assurance",
            "content": "<p>Our dedicated Quality team is with you on every step of the way. Insuring organic compliance and product quality. Analysis are performed on all incoming goods and we offer all required documentation and certification including a Certificate of Analysis for every lot you purchase.<\/p>",
            "button_label": "Read More",
            "button_link": "shopify:\/\/pages\/services",
            "button_color": "default"
          }
        },
        "09dbb847-aae0-44ec-be21-f3c1f92bbe1f": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/sqf-logo-lvl-2.png",
            "alt": "SQF Certification"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
